   "body" : "Busybox does not use locales - bitcoin should set a default C / Posix environment. The following locale error:\r\n\r\n    EXCEPTION: St13runtime_error       \r\n    locale::facet::_S_create_c_locale name not valid       \r\n    bitcoin in AppInit()       \r\n\r\n    terminate called after throwing an instance of 'std::runtime_error'\r\n      what():  locale::facet::_S_create_c_locale name not valid\r\n\r\nCan be fixed with the following patch https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/4147#issuecomment-42763464\r\n\r\nThe above patch is almost identical to the patch I proposed for Namecoin to fix this issue (Windows builds are unaffected):https://github.com/namecoin/namecoin/issues/72#issuecomment-42520429",
